timing_extract...ck_latency_arc(25.10)  timing_extract...ck_latency_arc(25.10)

Name
       timing_extract_model_ideal_clock_latency_arc

Syntax
       timing_extract_model_ideal_clock_latency_arc

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       When  set  to  true, the latency arcs for the generated clocks that are
       defined ideal are extracted with reference as master clock  during  ETM
       extraction.

       When set to false, the arcs are not extracted for generated clocks that
       are defined ideal during ETM extractions.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

